                                                     Donation Information
==========================================================================================================================

Donating will reward you with special privileges like: Beta Testing, Development, In-Game stuff, early game updates. Although, you must donate a certain amount for these rewards, but all donations are accepted. All donations will be used only for the development of the game.

Price Listings:
$5.00 - Access to game updates before update release*, Donator rank in forums

$10.00 - Access to game updates before update release*, Basic Donator rank in forums

$25.00 - Access to game updates up-to 3 days before update release, access to game within 1-2 weeks, Casual Donator rank in forums.

$50.00 - 25% discount on all In-Game items, access to game updates before up-to 6 days update release*, name put into credits, access to game within 24 hours, Mega Donator rank in forums.

$75.00 - 50% discount on all In-Game items, access to game updates up-to 9 days before official update release, name put into the credits, access to game immediately, Supreme Donator rank in forums.

$100.00 - 80% discount on all In-Game items, specially made clothing for character, special boosts(gameplay), name put in credits, access to game updates up-to 12 days before official update release, access to game instantly, Ultimate Donator rank in forums.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*this is only effective after major release of game. (Version 1 is released, and is taken out of Beta)
